<div class="founder-hero__content">

<div>

<h1 class="founder-hero__title">
Dr. Ahmed Kaffel
</h1>

<p class="founder-hero__subtitle">
Applied Mathematician · Computational Scientist · Engineering Research Leader
</p>

<p class="founder-hero__tagline">
