</a>

</div>

<div>

<img src="founder.jpg" class="founder-hero__photo">

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="elite-card">

<h3>Institutional Leadership</h3>

<p>

Dr. Ahmed Kaffel is Founder & Director of ITECCS, advancing applied mathematics, artificial intelligence, and scientific computing through research, consulting, and education.

</p>

</section>

</main>

<footer>

